data.meta_description: George is an experienced surgical assistant having assisted exclusively in the specialty of orthopaedic surgery for over 20 years..
data.text:
Dr Paul Nguyen graduated from Monash University in 2002, and spent time doing surgical training. He now works as a professional surgical assistant and has over 15 years of experience, specialising in orthopaedics, neurosurgery and general surgery.

He is a keen long distance runner and has participated in European races.

He looks forward to being of service to you.
